Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Only God knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to resume the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.06,0:06:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my guiding angels are here today, both in and out of body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask what I'm going to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.60,0:06:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My guiding angels are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.67,0:06:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So my guiding angels are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I don't take credit for anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:07:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So acknowledging the presence of divinity tends to reinforce when you affirm the presence
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.85,0:07:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity and give thanks to the Lord, you strengthen the guidance that you get from
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.99,0:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So acknowledging...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Acknowledging divinity as the source of your existence and thanking God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So giving thanks to God and acknowledging God tends to reinforce the divine energy within
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.76,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,your own psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So even in the pits of hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I was, like, forsaken forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it was forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, forever more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternally, you would be cut off from love or salvation forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the word forever, you got what forever means.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.95,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.43,0:08:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.98,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's when a voice from within me said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.79,0:08:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,if there is a God, I ask him for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of hell disappeared
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was suddenly in a radiance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.48,0:09:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,in which the divinity of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,shone forth like a radiant light from all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was over 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,900.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.21,0:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,950.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.19,0:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,945.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,950.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment was 945, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.14,0:09:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,From minus 500 or whatever it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,From 945's negative to 945's positive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.36,0:09:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:10:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity revealed itself as all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.37,0:10:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,To know that you are an expression of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an expression of divinity as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am an expression of divinity as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I can love God,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the beauty of the translator shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The beauty of the translator is shown as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.13,0:10:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no room for misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no room for misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you're very blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.26,0:10:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very blessed to have you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We are very blessed to have you with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dr. Moon and all our visitors
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because of them, this occasion arose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.45,0:11:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the charm of the Korean people came with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.59,0:11:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.11,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.85,0:11:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.11,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll go back to the slides, back to the mundane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From the sublime to the mundane, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.79,0:11:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, to become educated about the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.47,0:11:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and the subject of our lectures is a very singular discovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is very interesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the levels of consciousness and social problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's always presumed because of political gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,the political gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to blame it on society or blame it on a certain culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's the culture's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the culture's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.16,0:12:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it was the culture's fault,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,then everybody who grew up poor would be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, many people grew up poor, and they transcend to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,People that grew up rich often also become poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I keep forgetting he's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.51,0:13:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The levels of consciousness and the relationships of these things
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.70,0:13:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,are very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because for political gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,politicians keep on adding to the causes of culture or certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.32,0:13:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it's very interesting to study this relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.32,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:14:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.58,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, from this slide, we can stop blaming social conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the world is full of political gain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,by blaming one group for another group, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.17,0:14:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if we study these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,we can stop adding social responsibility to other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But all the difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the social difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.04,0:14:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the political difficulties,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,can be overcome by personal integrity and striving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.38,0:14:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anybody have any questions about this level that you see that
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,experientially what the people are doing is living out their own level of consciousness?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any questions about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What people are experiencing is their own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They are experiencing it as their own level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.57,0:15:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So, and this is why we say that you influence the world by what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what you are, then, is what influences the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,not by what you do or you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but by what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But by what you become.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the best thing we can do for our children, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.13,0:15:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is to try to provide for the advancement of their level of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So, there's a great benefit to a religious upbringing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual upbringing, spiritual integrus,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's Confucianism or Taoism or Buddhism or Christianity or Hindu,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,they all acknowledge a higher power and a gradient of being.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That you can become better than you are through endeavor and meditation and service to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.19,0:17:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, like a cork in water, you rise to your own level of buoyancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to be loving towards all of life in all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is the greatest gift you can give to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,So, when you see the little beetle,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.99,0:17:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I was talking about my little black beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When you see the little black beetle down there in the alley,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and you step around the beetle like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,the world is now a better place than if you went,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I always like to talk about this cockroach.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.35,0:17:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When the cockroach is on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,if you avoid it a little bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the world becomes a better place because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than stepping on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide, Eddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.16,0:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you can tell our students, they always walk over beetles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody who's been in these classes, they always step over the beetle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this is just reading the levels of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and the incidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.00,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll go to the next one, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.52,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the next section is on spiritual teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,about which there's a great deal of discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.39,0:19:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The next section is about spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.72,0:19:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of all the books and all the gurus
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and the famous and infamous teachers,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,the student is often confused which way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.45,0:19:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the reason that we need to know this is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because students and students of spiritual books
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,are always confused about spiritual teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.89,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And many questions we get in the mail, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,asked about a certain teacher, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.02,0:19:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what we try to do is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we publish the list of 100
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.93,0:19:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,integrous teachers over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a list of teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that we ask to measure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 20 teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:20:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And what level of, what is the level of their teaching, say, what is the level of their teaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So, a higher number doesn't necessarily mean that that teacher is better for you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Because a teacher who calibrates at 500 would be better for you than a teacher who calibrates at 800, but you don't understand anything he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we wanted to print out,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.98,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the characteristics that define the excellence of a teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,so that the student can become independent of the calibrated levels that they can learn for themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so we say that truth is not limited to the possession of only certain teachers or people, that it's really open to everyone. Truth is all-inclusive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Truth is not a possession of one particular teacher, and that it contains everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:21:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that it is available to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.24,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so truth is all-inclusive, and it's not given out as a secret.
