Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.13,0:22:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the exclusive property of any one religion or spiritual pathway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.91,0:22:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So there are great teachers in all the world's bona fide religions.
